{"tid":2503249,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"Art vs Design 你點揀？","createTime":"2021-04-25T02:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T23:18:47.000Z","uid":309438,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"27e152d24ce1e6772395daca564c31ef5eb81bf8","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"兩樣野係好唔同<br />\n但中間可以話有少少重疊位<br />\n我咁啱就踩咗係中間<br />\n<br />\nDesign 前景會清晰啲 我又讀得幾好<br />\nArt雖然難揾食 但我鍾意<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似經驗？<br />\n利申 宜家讀緊design 諗緊讀唔讀返art好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9d1a03f60b983e2bc8660e48e4ab92960b09e7","tid":2503249,"uid":122748,"like":9,"dislike":28,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"當art直接涉及商業價值，咪就係design"},{"pid":"958edf09f49e65558092924884ac697d5bac2ff8","tid":2503249,"uid":46388,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"兩樣野都唔好 兩樣野都q搵唔到食<br />\n襯早放棄最好一係轉去programme，一係轉去interior"},{"pid":"685b3ac7808989a9003a7bf19800369642eb618c","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"958edf09f49e65558092924884ac697d5bac2ff8","tid":2503249,"uid":46388,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"兩樣野都唔好 兩樣野都q搵唔到食<br />\n襯早放棄最好一係轉去programme，一係轉去interior"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T03:04:34.000Z","msg":"咁咪要重新讀過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚憎畫線<br />\nInterior冇乜可能"},{"pid":"e2057dee40b5538dffade08e25a31b4a1ffa37e5","tid":2503249,"uid":32837,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"讀鍾意果科 唔鐘意既話讀得好辛苦 加上2科都搵唔到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係知讀art將來可以做展覽果d工作"},{"pid":"d5336d044603f55e1efd570b0b8733eaa2dd3b92","tid":2503249,"uid":46388,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"685b3ac7808989a9003a7bf19800369642eb618c","tid":2503249,"uid