問下自己有無做苦行僧嘅心理準備先<br />\n返正職收工仲要做work，份人工唔高又要一邊支出你整work嘅使費<br />\n如果你做嘅嘢唔大路，要自己拓荒會更辛苦<br />\n<br />\n雖然話唔似design咁有老細出錢同俾要求你<br />\n但做art都唔係完全自由<br />\n你嘅個人情感/經驗/主題要搵方法link落大眾到<br />\n要令人覺得我都有個咁嘅感受/經歷<br />\n唔係嘅話整出嚟無人明都無用"},{"pid":"c185d424d194d2bb0e3f1d0c61dd79188ac91019","tid":2503249,"uid":154054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得係睇你屋企家底有幾厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da8782f4c6f491f4721b2cacadfb346820cf9dd","tid":2503249,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"668399fdb6b8b0f5c812065ab4208f8f5f5dfeb5","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48c62d92a63fe3289e15b7f4366be2160d87eb77","tid":2503249,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"興趣會揀art<br />\n利伸：讀design乞緊食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"咩design"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"讀Advertising <br />\n出來做緊graphic"},{"pid":"6245b22f914ec6ea07fa0fe8fbee6dd515e7a8b1","tid":2503249,"uid":279738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5286e47eec975a4b81dae0410f9bd0cc18521fa7","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633da4a5f0a61bdd59b94f4122ec5c41a7145e98","tid":2503249,"uid":251390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"樓主講多少少自己鐘意啲咩／睇開啲咩？<br />\n讀緊U？<br />\n利申做緊藝術相關行業"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"宜家讀緊design <br />\n自己係鍾意畫畫同做artwork 多過對住電腦對客做design 嘅<br />\n覺得成件事太功利 但我讀意外又讀得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都係想讀art 多啲<br />\n你係做緊咩？<br />\n我有諗過同人夾開studios  之後兩邊走 <br />\n得閒可以接freelance 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re