/>\n<br />\nArt同Design兩樣野唔同既係前者係serve自己concept , idea , visualisation<br />\n<br />\n後者係train problem solving skill, shape language, visual communication <br />\n用form and shape 黎deliver message"},{"pid":"2f54fae787cca23c982969c94352778821242667","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8c989104456bff9a58ca63122e7eacf6fc98be3","tid":2503249,"uid":69866,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">design = 生前有錢<br />\nart = 死後有錢</span><br />\n<br />\n藝術層次高,平凡人唔識. 價值靠拍賣會決定<br />\n<br />\ndesign 俾平常人用, 價值取決於大眾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:52:32.000Z","msg":"以前係<br />\n<br />\n但現代社會好多野都已經用唔到一套理論/論述去解釋<br />\n<br />\n個世界愈嚟愈痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc9cd0ced6cb397d0546d30b1e3e9af6e5c47a0","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76384295f9fe07feb4499a5a8120e2a82d10dd50","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ff9d1a03f60b983e2bc8660e48e4ab92960b09e7","tid":2503249,"uid":122748,"like":9,"dislike":28,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"當art直接涉及商業價值，咪就係design"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"唔一定？<br />\n唔知喎 咁賣artwork 都叫designs?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:53:19.000Z","msg":"任何畫作既planning都要design過"},{"pid":"7f228fae7f68655859d7e87c8886f0ba4bd1de81","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00eb073f9979305aed21cc69ea0d92e1d14641bf","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cafccb63274722cb42844784b81bf729c68ea30","tid":2503249,"uid":202514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:16:48.000Z","msg":"如果你好確定自己唔想做designer咁就讀art<br />\n同埋睇你鍾意做啲咩主題同方式<br />\n<br />\n比如我自己鍾意做啲個人情感出發嘅嘢<br />\n而且著重個形式/過程多過成品<br />\n所以就無理前景揀左art<br />\n<br />\n你揀一科自己鍾意嘅<br />\n就算到時諗idea同點做嗰陣要Push得自己好勁都唔會覺得後悔揀咗呢邊<br />\n<span class=\"small\">信我，構思嗰陣係咁鑽牛角尖好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果諗住做art搵食嘅話<br />\n問下自己有無做苦行僧嘅心理準備先<br />\n返正職收工仲要做work，份人工唔高又要一邊支出你整work嘅使費<br />\n如果你做嘅嘢唔大路，要自己拓荒會更辛苦<br />\n<br />\n雖然話唔似design咁有老細出錢同俾要求你<br />\n但做art都唔係完全自由<br />\n你嘅個人情感/經驗/主題要搵方法link落大眾到<br />\n要令人覺得我都有個咁嘅感受/經歷<br />\n唔係嘅話整出嚟無人明都無用"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n我好鍾意諗作品意念 同你一樣鍾意過程多過成品 不過成品整好咗嗰吓都好滿足<br />\n有諗過過台灣 起碼好過香港文化沙漠<br />\n香港除咗開ig po畫連結大眾 好似門小雷咁 我諗唔到我仲要點 不過要出名好撚難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:56:08.000Z","msg":"出名都有運氣既加成嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天時地利人和"},{"pid":"fddf43d89ca600456ec4cb9bbeebcb546c275a6d","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92926d483bbb69509256420fa7143e411b228d81","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2e7244f2c88eddc6436b2b3d298915fddc257b60","tid":2503249,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4351648ac4836a72bd975576106b4b19c68ecf63","tid":2503249,"uid":309438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"好撚窮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"好窮仲讀art/design<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"讀咗咁耐 點撚樣轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我除咗art 冇樣識啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:56:58.000Z","msg":"識係搵到食既程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"5673f5321a51d2e051cda5dd26958715beabf9f4","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afdb8d7964d533821ea68a9f19dc7d08ad0054cf","tid":2503249,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"ART係天份<br />\nDESIGN係人脈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:59:53.000Z","msg":"藝術一樣被人脈關係影響<br />\n唔係既啲人讀ACCD為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96503db20aa7f0d18328c16d7cdb87e979fcc8b","tid":2503249,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:00:35.000Z","msg":"讀完Art做博物館都係一條出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880a7710ccfee3cef8d992f243074da8c4e6e9ab","tid":2503249,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5673f5321a51d2e051cda5dd26958715beabf9f4","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afdb8d7964d533821ea68a9f19dc7d08ad0054cf","tid":2503249,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"ART係天份<br />\nDESIGN係人脈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:59:53.000Z","msg":"藝術一樣被人脈關係影響<br />\n唔係既啲人讀ACCD為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:02:12.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇乜工係唔需要人脈"},{"pid":"a303afe00397d5dcad2f22bf6b6ec0b40ead83fb","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b77ff768714e7a13e02e9d4c334e43b7edfa19c","tid":2503249,"uid":127469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:11:13.000Z","msg":"讀Art呢類好易會後悔，除非你屋企同你都冇壓力負擔<br />\n我都係讀類似嘅科出身，從事緊類似嘅行業，可以分享下出路<br />\n<br />\n不過首先想強調，好認同樓上有人提到，為興趣嘅話，千祈唔好去讀，因為換嚟嘅只有痛苦同浪費咗幾年嘅光陰<br />\n當興趣變成咗career之後，要嘅唔係passion，而係devotion，因為passion有燒晒嘅一日，但devotion就唔同，係一種好難動搖嘅信仰， 就好似樓上有人提到，係近乎宗教式嘅苦行，要有無條件犧牲好多野嘅心理準備<br />\n<br />\n讀完出嚟基本上係有三個大方向<br />\n<br />\n一係就走向商業主流，揾唔到食之餘仲要受氣。所謂揾唔到食未必係生存唔到，而係同同輩嘅人嘅收入有極顯著嘅差距，要終日為生活積蓄而憂心。就當揾到食，都係付出緊比其他人更多嘅努力，去獲得同樣甚至更少嘅報酬，而且同一般工作唔同，做呢類工作好難睇清楚向上流動嘅機會。最慘係你未必係做緊你原先想做嘅野，已經委曲求存，但都係僅僅有啖飯暖吓肚<br />\n<br />\n二就係繼續做返本身想做嘅野，但係就預咗曲高和寡，平日乞食為主，要靠兼職開飯<br />\n<br />\n然後就係三，最多係呢個類別，就係先後經歷過以上兩個階段之後，開始心諗做得咁辛苦，受晒氣都幾乎冇飯開，又睇唔到前景，到底呢一切係為咗咩？於是把心一橫去做返比較正常工作，例如係開班或者入學校教書、有啲就做完全唔關事嘅正職 / 兼職<br />\n<br />\n好多本身係諗住工餘時搞返創作，但我識嘅人大部分都做唔到，因為工作已經好heavy load，而且去到呢個階段多數都差不多三十，開始組織家庭，家中長輩亦年紀漸老，變咗有好多金錢同心理負擔要兼顧<br />\n<br />\n我係過來人，身邊亦識好多過來人，我諗有七八成以上唔會做返本行，留低嗰啲一係屋企有錢，一係喺主流圈子r到啖飯食平步青雲，一係就好捱得乞食要人接濟嘅日子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:03:30.000Z","msg":"問心<br />\n講真中國撈藝術好過香港<br />\n當你要搵食真係好難唔做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac766d518027fe36d8955ea18b4e0938624a649","tid":2503249,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"395b8d5b76f4422091f745c8e91129bdf278f043","tid":2503249,"uid":15323,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"兩個都係等乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過來人乞左7年先30k<br />\n肝已爛，自己諗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:04:15.000Z","msg":"30k好撚高啦"},{"pid":"a4bc97368ca446818e5fe3886716d383c85ce4b1","tid":2503249,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ac766d518027fe36d8955ea18b4e0938624a649","tid":2503249,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"395b8d5b76f4422091f745c8e91129bdf278f043","tid":2503249,"uid":15323,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"兩個都係等乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過來人乞左7年先30k<br />\n肝已爛，自己諗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:04:15.000Z","msg":"30k好撚高啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:06:08.000Z","msg":"當你OT當食生菜你都應該過唔到五十歲"}]}